{
  "video_id": "vXDJ-nAykKE",
  "title": "Jonathan Drori: Every pollen grain has a story",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "Thank you. I have two missions here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "The first is to tell you something about pollen, I hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "and to convince you that it&#39;s more than just something that gets up your nose."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "And, secondly, to convince you"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "that every home really ought to have a scanning electron microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "Pollen is a flower&#39;s way of making more flowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "It carries male sex cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "from one flower to another."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "This gives us genetic diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "or at least it gives the plants genetic diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s really rather better not to mate with yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s probably true of humans as well, mostly."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "Pollen is produced by the anthers of flowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "Each anther can carry up to 100,000 grains of pollen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "so, it&#39;s quite prolific stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "And it isn&#39;t just bright flowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 67259.0,
      "text": "that have pollen; it&#39;s also trees and grasses."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "And remember that all our cereal crops are grasses as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Here is a scanning electron micrograph of a grain of pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "The little hole in the middle, we&#39;ll come to a bit later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s for the pollen tube"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "to come out later on. A very tiny tube."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s 20 micrometers across,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "that pollen grain there."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s about a 50th of a millimeter."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "But not all pollen is quite so simple looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "This is Morina. This is a plant --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;ve always thought to be rather tedious --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "named after Morin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "who was an enterprising French gardener,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "who issued the first seed catalog"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "in 1621."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "But anyway, take a look at its pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "This is amazing, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "That little hole in the middle there is for the pollen tube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "and when the pollen finds its special female spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "in another Morina flower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "just on the right species, what happens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "Like I said, pollen carries the male sex cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "If you actually didn&#39;t realize that plants have sex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "they have rampant, promiscuous"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "and really quite interesting and curious sex. Really."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) A lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "My story is actually not about plant propagation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "but about pollen itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "\"So, what are pollen&#39;s properties?\" I hear you ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "First of all, pollen is tiny. Yes we know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also very biologically active,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "as anyone with hay fever will understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "Now, pollen from plants, which are wind-dispersed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "like trees and grasses and so on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "tend to cause the most hay fever."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "And the reason for that is they&#39;ve got to chuck out"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "masses and masses of pollen to have any chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "of the pollen reaching another plant of the same species."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "Here are some examples --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re very smooth if you look at them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "of tree pollen that is meant to be carried by the wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "Again -- this time, sycamore -- wind-dispersed."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "So, trees: very boring flowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "not really trying to attract insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "Cool pollen, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "This one I particularly like."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "This is the Monterey Pine, which has little air sacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "to make the pollen carry even further."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "Remember, that thing is just about 30 micrometers across."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s much more efficient if you can get insects to do your bidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "This is a bee&#39;s leg"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "with the pollen glommed onto it from a mallow plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "And this is the outrageous and beautiful"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "flower of the mangrove palm."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "Very showy, to attract lots of insects to do its bidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "The pollen has little barbs on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "if we look."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "Now, those little barbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "obviously stick to the insects well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "but there is something else that we can tell from this photograph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "and that is that you might be able to see a fracture line"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "across what would be the equator of this, if it was the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "That tells me that it&#39;s actually been fossilized, this pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m rather proud to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "that this was found just near London, and that 55 million years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "London was full of mangroves."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t that cool?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "Okay, so this is another species evolved to be dispersed by insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "You can tell that from the little barbs on there."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "All these pictures were taken with a scanning electron microscope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "actually in the lab at Kew Laboratories."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "No coincidence that these were taken"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "by Rob Kesseler, who is an artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "and I think it&#39;s someone with a design and artistic eye"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "like him that has managed to bring out the best in pollen."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "Now, all this diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "means that you can look at a pollen grain"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "and tell what species it came from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s actually quite handy if you"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "maybe have a sample and you want to see where it came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "So, different species of plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "grow in different places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "and some pollen carries further than others."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "So, if you have a pollen sample,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "then in principle, you should be able to tell"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "where that sample came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "And this is where it gets interesting for forensics."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "Pollen is tiny. It gets on to things, and it sticks to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "So, not only does each type of pollen look different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "but each habitat has a different combination of plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "A different pollen signature, if you like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "or a different pollen fingerprint."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "By looking at the proportions and combinations"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "of different kinds of pollen in a sample,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "you can tell very precisely where it came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "This is some pollen embedded in a cotton shirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "similar to the one that I&#39;m wearing now."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "Now, much of the pollen will still be there"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "after repeated washings."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "Where has it been?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "Four very different habitats might look similar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;ve got very different pollen signatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "Actually this one is particularly easy, these pictures were all taken"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "in different countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "But pollen forensics can be very subtle."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s being used now to track"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "where counterfeit drugs have been made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "where banknotes have come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "to look at the provenance of antiques"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "and see that they really did come from the place"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "the seller said they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "And murder suspects have been tracked"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "using their clothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "certainly in the U.K., to within an area"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s small enough that you can send in tracker dogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "to find the murder victim."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "So, you can tell from a piece of clothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "to within about a kilometer or so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "where that piece of clothing has been recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "and then send in dogs."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "And finally, in a rather grizzly way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "the Bosnia war crimes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "some of the people brought to trial were brought to trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "because of the evidence from pollen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "which showed that bodies had been buried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "exhumed and then reburied somewhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "I hope I&#39;ve opened your eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;ll excuse the visual pun, (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "to some of pollen&#39;s secrets."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "This is a horse chestnut."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "There is an invisible beauty all around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "each grain with a story to tell ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "each of us, in fact, with a story to tell"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "from the pollen fingerprint that&#39;s upon us."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "Thank you to the colleagues at Kew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "and thank you to palynologists everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}